Here are all the alternative solutions, from easiest to most involved:

Why This Error Occurs
Your Google Workspace org (likely managed by NIC or MeitY IT) has an Organisation Policy set:

constraints/iam.disableServiceAccountKeyCreation = TRUE
This blocks all users from downloading JSON keys — even project owners and admins.

Solution Options — Choose One
Option 1 — Ask Your Org Admin to Exempt Your Project (Easiest)
This is the fastest path. Your Google Workspace admin can create a policy exception for just your project without changing the org-wide rule.

What to send to your IT/GCP admin:

"Please exempt project negd-dashboard-pipeline from the org policy constraints/iam.disableServiceAccountKeyCreation. We need a service account JSON key for the NeGD automated dashboard pipeline. Alternatively, please create the key on our behalf and share it securely."

